        <pbpko:IAO_0000115 xml:lang="en">zip is a format standard of a digital entity that is conformant with the PKWARE .ZIP file format specification  (http://www.pkware.com/index.php?option=com_content&amp;task=view&amp;id=59&amp;Itemid=103/)</pbpko:IAO_0000115>
